NAME

  Portable BBS

DESCRIPTION

  This is simple web application example which have following features.
  
  - Web framework is Mojolicious
  - Database is SQLite
  - O/R mapper is DBIx::Custom
  - Easy setup system by Test::ModuleVersion.
    you can install CPAN module easily and can specify module version. 

What you can learn from this application?

  - Mojolicious frame work. routing, template, and controller
  - SQLite
  - DBIx::Custom
  - How to use Test::ModuleVersion to create portable web application

